title: Doubt
content: I got 25xx rank in my pessat exam 2024. I am getting cs at ec campus and I will not be able to attend 1st counseling, so will there be seat available for cs at ec campus in 2nd round counseling?

comments.body:
The number of people who take the seat and then leave before second round will be the number of remaining seats. 

Nobody can say how many that is.
Dude last year in second round seats went into negatives..as there was an overbooking of seats like none left the seat after round 1. So imo 2nd round counselling is just for name sake
